<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A. &amp; Taeger, A." box="[1055,1350,1517,1543]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75" pagination="31 - 40" refId="ref78859" refString="Shinohara, A. &amp; Taeger, A. (2007) Description of a new species and collection data of pamphiliid sawflies (Insecta, Hymenoptera, Symphyta) mainly from the Russian Far East. Bulletin of the National Museum of Nature and Science, Tokyo, Series A, 33, 31 - 40." type="journal article" year="2007">Shinohara &amp; Taeger 2007</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
